                  <msItem>
                     <p>West-Haddon.

   Condition of a bond in 20 marks from <persName nymRef="Knyth">
                           <forename>John</forename> son of <persName>
                              <forename>William</forename> 
                              <surname>Knyth</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108032">West Haddon</placeName>
                           </persName>
                        </persName>, to <persName nymRef="Knyth">his brother <forename>Thomas</forename>
                        </persName>, viz. to save harmless his said brother from all services, &amp;c., for the lands, &amp;c., in <placeName key="place_108032">W<supplied>est</supplied> H<supplied>addon</supplied>
                        </placeName> late of <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Knyth</surname>
                        </persName> their father. 
   Witnesses: <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Andrew</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> 
                           <surname>Ormond</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Thomas</forename> 
                           <surname>Asscheby</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Warde</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> 
                           <surname>Andrew</surname>
                        </persName>,
   <persName>
                           <forename>Thomas</forename> 
                           <surname>Thomas</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108032">W<supplied>est</supplied> H<supplied>addon</supplied>
                           </placeName>
                        </persName>. 
   <origDate notBefore="1421-04-11">
                           <supplied>After 11 April 1421.</supplied>
                        </origDate>
                     </p>
                  </msItem>
